data.description: Looking for a home with a spacious yard to call your own? Look no further! This property includes multiple parcels of land behind the property, giving you the freedom to create your dream outdoor space as you see fit.  Step into your new beginning and let your senses be enchanted by this beautifully updated Bi-Level home in Twinsburg Township. This spacious abode boasts an updated kitchen adorned with granite counters, updated cabinets, and stainless-steel appliances that will inspire your culinary adventures. The pristine windows with natural light, enhancing the updated flooring's beauty. The main level features three bedrooms that share an updated full bath, complete with ceramic tiled shower and flooring. It's a serene retreat you'll adore. As you descend to the lower level, discover a family room and a bonus room that offers endless possibilities, whether it's for an additional bedroom, TV, gaming, a playroom, home office, or your own creative vision. The choices are yours to make. Step outside onto the patio or deck, where you can bask in the warmth of summer days and create cherished memories. This home has received recent updates including new windows on lower level, new flooring, fresh paint, and more ensuring it's ready for your personal touch. Its prime location provides easy access to highways, shopping, and more. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your own. Call today to schedule your private showing and embark on this exciting journey towards your new home!
